according to the official doc, "pulsar-admin functions list" is support by the functions-worker, and in functions-worker's config file(functions_worker.yml), the workerPort is 6750 and workerPortTls is 6751.&nbsp;

when i use 6750, "pulsar-admin functions list" is unavailable, but "pulsar-admin sinks list" works. and other cmd just like "pulsar-admin functions get/state/stats" works well, that why i am confused.




