> Actually, I have solved this problem by editing "advertisedAddress" configuration in standalone.conf.
@fangpengcheng95  right, you need `advertisedAddress` setting in conf file. or use command like: `bin/pulsar standalone -a 127.0.0.1` to assign the advertisedAddress. 

